{
  "bookId": "heshanggong-laozi",
  "num": 50,
  "title": "第五十章（貴生）",
  "author": "老子",
  "authorId": "Laozi",
  "dynasty": "周",
  "era": "周",
  "genre": "prose",
  "verses": [
    {
      "text": "出生入死。"
    },
    {
      "text": "生之徒十有三，死之徒死十有三，"
    },
    {
      "text": "人之生，動之死地十有三。"
    },
    {
      "text": "夫何故，"
    },
    {
      "text": "以其求生之厚。"
    },
    {
      "text": "蓋以聞善攝生者，"
    },
    {
      "text": "路行不遇兕虎，"
    },
    {
      "text": "入軍不披甲兵，"
    },
    {
      "text": "兕無投其角，虎無所措爪，兵無所容其刃。"
    },
    {
      "text": "夫何故，"
    },
    {
      "text": "以其無死地。"
    }
  ],
  "sections": {},
  "annotations": [],
  "layers": {
    "heshanggong": [
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-1",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 5
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "出生，謂情欲出五內，魂靜魄定，故生。 入死，謂情欲入於胸臆，精勞神惑，故死。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-2",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 15
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "言生死之類各有十三，謂九竅四關也。 其生也目不妄視，耳不妄聽，鼻不妄嗅，口不妄言，味，手不妄持，足不妄行，精神不妄施。其死也反是也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-3",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 2,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 12
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "人知求生，動作反之十三死也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-4",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 3,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 4
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "問何故動之死地也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-5",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 4,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 7
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "所以動之死地者，以其求生活之事太厚，違道忤天，妄行失紀。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-6",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 5,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 8
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "攝，養也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-7",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 6,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 7
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "自然遠離，害不干也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-8",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 7,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 7
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "不好戰以殺人。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-9",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 8,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 19
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "養生之人，兕虎無由傷，兵刃無從加之也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-10",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 9,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 4
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "問兕虎兵甲何故不加害之。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-11",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 10,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 6
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "以其不犯十三之死地也。言神明營護之，此物不敢害。",
        "source": "cham"
      }
    ]
  },
